  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/10/microsoft-gives-developers-early-access-to-finished-windows-8-1/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/09/screenshot-33.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n之前微软<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/27/microsoft-windows-8-1-rtm/\">向电脑厂商发放</a> <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/26/windows-8-1-hands-on/\">Windows 8.1</a> 时，部分开发者就不太开心，因为他们没有像往年一样提前收到软件来优化自己的 App。如今微软显然是听到了抱怨的声音，于是在今天，他们宣布将向 MSDN 和 TechNet 会员发放 RTM 版本的 Windows 8.1、8.1 专业版以及 Windows Server 2012 R2。<br />\n<br />\n据悉企业版本将会在九月晚些时候对开发者开放，而普通用户则仍需等到十月中旬。值得一提的是，今天微软在 <a href=\"http://blogs.skype.com/2013/09/09/skype-pre-release-arrives-on-windows-8-1/\">Skype 博客</a>中再次强调了 Windows 8.1 将会「内建完整的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/15/windows-8-1-ships-with-skype-pre-installed/\">Skype</a> App」，包括锁幕下接听来电、自动调整链接弹出视窗大小、IE 中直接点击通话等新功能很快就会与大家见面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/09/09/microsoft-gives-developers-early-access-to-finished-windows-8-1/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://blogs.windows.com/windows/b/bloggingwindows/archive/2013/09/09/download-windows-8-1-rtm-visual-studio-2013-rc-and-windows-server-2012-r2-rtm-today.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Blogging Windows</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://blogs.msdn.com/b/stevengu/archive/2013/09/09/download-windows-8-1-rtm-visual-studio-2013-rc-and-windows-server-2012-r2-rtm-today.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">MSDN Blogs</a>、<a href=\"http://blogs.skype.com/2013/09/09/skype-pre-release-arrives-on-windows-8-1/\" target=\"_blank\">Skype Blog</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/10/microsoft-gives-developers-early-access-to-finished-windows-8-1/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanen